It used to check the information of disk usage of files and directories on a machine.

$ du
$ du --time
$ du -h                                                                           # can see sizes in Bytes, Kilobytes, Megabytes, Gigabytes, etc
$ du -a                                                                           # displays the disk usage of all the files and directories
$ du -s
$ du -sh                                                                          # total disk usage size of a directory
$ du -ha --time                                                                   # display the disk usage based on a modification of time
$ du /FOLDER_NAME
$ du -h /FOLDER_NAME
$ du -a /FOLDER_NAME/FOLDER_NAME
$ du -sh /FOLDER_NAME
$ du -ha --time /FOLDER_NAME/FOLDER_NAME
